
PiB v0.2 - Python Build System
------------------------------

Project Homepage: http://donw.org/b/?d=PiB

For a more in-depth discussion of the origins of this build system, check out the following  blog post:

	http://donw.org/b/?d=2011-06-28-17-04-00

To install, ensure that the Python interpreter is invoked whenever you execute a .py file from the
command-prompt and that the PiB Python directory is in your PATH.

This project will be updated continuously as my needs for it change :)